  "keyFeatures": [
    "Four core kinetic models: Constitutive, Tet-Off, Chemogenetic, and Oscillating RMA",
    "Dual Rust and Python API — high-performance core with ergonomic Python bindings via PyO3",
    "Pharmacokinetic sub-models for doxycycline (dox) and clozapine-N-oxide (CNO)",
    "Multiple ODE solvers including Dopri5, Kvaerno3, and RungeKutta4",
    "Stochastic simulation support for the constitutive model",
    "numpy-compatible Solution objects for downstream analysis",
    "Graphical web and desktop application for interactive model exploration",
    "Published on crates.io as rma_kinetics"
  ],
